'''''gwing''''' is a noun meaning "foam" or "spray" in [[Sindarin]]. Compare with ''[[winga]]'' in [[Quenya]].

==Examples==
* ''[[Elwing]]'' = "Star-spray"
* ''[[Vingilot]]'' = "Foam-flower"
